    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "purpose feels like such a joke though. like, just trying to 'redefine' things doesn't change the fact that the universe is cold and indifferent. it's just a way to distract ourselves from the truth. why bother building something new when the end result is always just nothingness?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
